                          "code": "\t#filter \u003d {\u0027typeFilter\u0027:typeFilter,\u0027engineFilter\u0027:engineFilter}\n\tif value and value !\u003d 0:\n\t\ttypeFilter \u003d value[\u0027typeFilter\u0027]\n\t\tengineFilter \u003d value[\u0027engineFilter\u0027]\n\t\toptype \u003d BlueRidge.Config.OperationType.getOne(typeFilter)\n\t\tentype \u003d BlueRidge.Config.Engine.getOne(engineFilter)\n\t\topName \u003d optype.get(\u0027name\u0027)\n\t\tenName \u003d entype.get(\u0027name\u0027)\n\t\tresp \u003d \u0027Filter: \u0027\n\t\tif opName:\n\t\t\tresp +\u003d \u0027{} \u0027.format(opName)\n\t\tif enName:\n\t\t\tresp +\u003d \u0027{}\u0027.format(enName)\n\telse:\n\t\tresp \u003d \u0027\u0027\n\treturn resp",
